headline: M&T Bank Named Founding Sponsor of CenterState CEO's INSPYRE Innovation Hub, the Largest Business Accelerator in New York State
summary: M&T Bank (NYSE:MTB) announced it will become the Founding Sponsor of CenterState CEO's INSPYRE Innovation Hub in downtown Syracuse. This long-term sponsorship with CenterState CEO, an independent, nonprofit organization focused on growing the economy and supporting businesses across Central New York, will expand efforts to accelerate entrepreneurism and startup growth, cultivate industry-disrupting technology and fuel the region's ecosystem for talent development and attraction.
